Summary: 
 * Merge from SysteMoC--devel--0.8
 - Removed superflous virtual inheritance from sc_interface for
   smoc_chan_in_base_if and smoc_chan_out_base_if.
 - Centralized guard evaluation with channel interface in smoc_chan_if.hpp.
   Removed all the code responsible for guard evaluation from smoc_root_port.hpp.
 - Undo: Moved interface dependent operations from
     smoc_sysc_port to smoc_port_base (-> cache interface
     there, not in smoc_sysc_port to avoid dynamic_cast
     on each access!)
   dynamic cast will later be replaced by a static_cast
   after virtual inheritance for smoc_chan_(in|out)_if
   has been deleted. Furthermore we need the interface
   to be stored in smoc_sysc_port which is port data type
   independent and used by guard evaluation which itself
   is data type independent!

